{"_path":"/resident/r031","_dir":"resident","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"A7重劃區公車規劃提案","description":null,"image":"/images/resident/r031-05.jpeg","sequence":31,"category":"交通建設","place":"A7重劃區","author":"社區網站","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2025 "},{"name":"og:title","content":"社區網站-地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-03-06T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"a7-重劃區公車規劃提案"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區公車規劃提案"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"主旨"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主旨"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區居住人口快速增加中，加上郵政物流園區及樂善科技園區的人員進駐都會造成區域交通無法負荷需要盡速做好整體交通規劃。\n本提案希望推動 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 區域公車的整合規劃及建構"}]},{"type":"text","value":", 並作為未來"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山輕軌捷運建構的參考"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"說明"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"說明"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"a7-人口成長速度超過預期"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 人口成長速度超過預期"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"人口數快速增長："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"根據樂居網資訊，A7 重劃區人口數增幅超越房屋數量增長。2017 年 12 月，A7 重劃區總人口數約 1.6 萬人。 至 2024 年 5 月底，人口數已接近 3.5 萬人，人口數翻倍。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"內政部原預計 A7 重劃區至 2031 年容納人口數為 3.5 萬人，但此"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目標提前 7 年達成，顯示人口遷入速度遠超政府預期"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"捷運站運量："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園捷運統計顯示，A7 體育大學站進出站人次大幅增加。2017 年 12 月，日平均進出站人次為 1,624 人。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"至 2024 年 6 月，日平均進出站人次達到 11,120 人，"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"增幅達 685%"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"備注: 上面數據依據 Gemini 提供, 如有誤請指正！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"區域大眾運輸的需求"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"區域大眾運輸的需求"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區涵蓋面積較大，多數的社區及區域內科技園區公司距離機捷 A7/A8 站都較遠, 需要最後一哩的接駁。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前 Ubike 站點已經廣泛佈建了，但區域道路並沒有完善的自行車道規劃，現有道路也很難建置自行車專用道！ 大量鼓勵 Ubike 的騎乘是不切實際。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"多數科技園區公司都有接駁車接送員工上下班, 但目前與居民及公司的私家車已經造成交通尖峰時段的交通過負荷！ 希望能提升大眾運輸公車或輕軌捷運才能舒緩區域交通問題。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"辦法建議-草擬"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"辦法建議 - 草擬"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"公車站點的配置改善建議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車站點的配置改善建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"現階段的公車站點標示如下圖, 目前樂善/郵政物流園區 及 文青國中小 區域都是缺少公車進入的區域。 建議先規劃建置 郵政物流站 及 文青國小站 (藍色標示)。 讓 A7 重劃區的公車路線佈建能有整體完整的規劃。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r031-05.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r031-05.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"公車站的路線及頻率整理及檢討"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車站的路線及頻率整理及檢討"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區現有的區域公車包含: "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"202, 603, 606, 607 及 桃園樂活巴士 L317/L317A, L318, L319/L319A, L326, L327"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n穿越 A7 重劃區的公車包含: "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"708/708A, 786/786 區, 858, 967/967 直, 5057, 5065"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n詳細資料請參考 A7 社區網站-城市探索： "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://a7kanban15.netlify.app/transportation"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A7 重劃區 交通指南"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以下將依據各生活區鄰近的站點分別檢討公車路線及頻率需求："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善國小生活圈"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善公園站"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車路線包含: 202, L317/L317A, L318, L319/L319A, L326, L327"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上班尖峰時段 有多條樂活巴士彌補 202 班次不足的問題。但其餘時段去程/體育大學只有 7 個班次/天 返程/工四工業區只有 5 個班次 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"居民希望增加班次頻率以提升搭乘意願"}]},{"type":"text","value":"！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"202 班車多數為低底盤車種, 可以方便輪椅, 嬰兒車及 攜帶大型行李的旅客，值的推廣到其他路線。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善國小站"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車路線包含: 202, 606, 607"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"606 與 607 班次如何脫善錯開，本站平均 15 分鐘內可以有一班車。 方便樂善國小生活圈居民前往生活機能更完整的合宜住宅，也便利了前往樟腦寮步道登山的居民。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望 606 能仿造 202 採用低底盤車種, 方便輪椅, 嬰兒車 及買菜拖車上下。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"郵政物流生活圈"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n郵政物流站: 待建置"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中心商業生活圈"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n文化一樂善二路口站"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車路線包含:"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"體育大學站"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車路線包含: 202, 603, 606, 607, 5065, 967/967 直 L317/L317A, L318, L319/L319A"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"居民希望增加 967 到桃園酒廠的班次能延伸到體育大學"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 讓文化一路 A7 重劃區路段能有更多的聯通公車。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"希望由 A7 體育大學站到 長庚大學/體育大學路段能建立 自行車專用車道或人車共道, 鼓勵學生使用 Ubike, 也應將人行道徹底整理平整！"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文青國小生活圈"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n文青國小站: 待建置"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"體育大學生活圈"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n文學路口站"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公車路線包含: 202, 606, 607"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"區域公車路線修訂建議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"區域公車路線修訂建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"方案一：606 路線修訂建議"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"為將大眾運輸公車涵蓋 極為重要的 郵政物流生活圈 及 文青國小生活圈, 建議修訂 606 公車路線。 如下圖所示："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新增郵政物流站及文青國小站, 讓公車能普及到這兩個區域。滿足這兩生活圈的社區居民需求, 包含郵政物流生活圈學童前往文青國小及居民前往機捷 A7 站。同時可以解決樂善科學園區及郵政物流園區的通勤接駁。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"需要建立 606 雙向通車, 以免讓兩個生活圈只有單向可通的困擾。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r031-06.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r031-06.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"方案二: 603 路線修訂建議"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提升體育大學生活圈學童到文青國小的便利性。也讓文青國小生活圈居民能前往機捷 A7 站。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"新增的文青國小站雖然與原有的"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文桃牛角坡路口站"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 或 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文化一樂善二路口站"}]},{"type":"text","value":"不遠, 但"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"考量回程幼兒需要穿越主幹道文桃路或文化一路的安全問題"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"603 公車增加文青國小多停一站, 原有行車路線的長度與時間都不影響的前提"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 是考量客運公司目前可能缺駕駛及車輛。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"r031-01.jpeg","src":"/images/resident/r031-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"聯外公車延伸修訂建議"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"聯外公車延伸/修訂建議"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由於三重客運總站在華亞園區/公西站, 聯外的公車如 708, 786, 858 如能將"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"終點由華亞園區延伸至 A7 體育大學站"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 就能大幅改善 A7 重劃區的直達聯外區域, 包含"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"708 直達 南崁, 台茂購物中心"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"786 直達 林口三井 Outlet 購物中心, 林口國中, 師大林口分校"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"858 直達 林口三井 Outlet 購物中心, 樹林火車站"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"967 公車目前有許多班次只到達桃園酒廠, 而且非直達車需要繞行林口"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"967 直達 台北市政府, 希望能將所有班次都延伸到體育大學, 並儘量增加 967 直達車的班次，避免繞行林口區域。未來能成為龜山區的專屬公車。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"附錄"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"附錄"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"立委即時處理結果"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"立委即時處理結果"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1CC3YBVEQw/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"牛煦庭 立委 FB 2025/03/06"}]},{"type":"text","value":":\n經過與市府交通局討論， 牛煦庭在 2025/03/06 協調確認，三重客運會增購新型中巴， "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"投入 607 的營運！多一輛車出勤，一天將帶來 6 個新班次，"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 增加服務量能，造福坪頂與大迴龍通勤族。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"非常感謝小牛委員能迅速處理龜山鄉親的交通需求。感謝你！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"網友意見匯總"},"children"